game.name: Pregnant Anna Surgery
game.description:
Your favorite princess Anna is pregnant and she is ready to deliver a baby in the operation theatre. However, suddenly she got an injury this morning, which has created a need of going through a surgery on an urgent basis. She would have a cute and lovely baby today. Are you able to provide this pregnant lady with the needful treatment? Join Pregnant Anna Surgery and get ready to take care of all responsibilities a doctor need to perform during the surgery!

Now it will be in your hands to save her and her baby life with the help of the given things. Providing this woman with the first aid timely will also allow her to give a safe birth of a cute baby. Use the tissue paper to wipe out the blood, puss shown on the outside of her body! Follow the instructions and use all the medical tools, including stethoscope, scissor, injection and x-ray! Make sure that you would also use the bandage on her infected part. 

When you are done your entire job, do not forget to give her a pill that could help her recover fast after the delivery. She will be happy to see her baby in her hand and grateful to you for your kind efforts. Good luck for a happy and safe delivery of her child in our new html5 surgery game! Try to browse through our extensive world of free doctor games to improve your doctoring skills in a friendly environment!
